  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Mehlala ya khoutu, Disekema tsa JSON, le diteplete tsa maano tse balehang ke mochini di na le laesense ya MIT ntle le ha ho boletswe ka tsela e nngwe. O ka di sebedisa sebakeng sa hao ka bolokolohi.",
