  "Commercial use requires contact": "Tshebediso ya kgwebo e hloka hore ho ikopanngwe le rona",
  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "E laetswe kamora Bletchley AI Safety Summit mme e etelletswe pele ke Yoshua Bengio ka thuso ya ditsebi tse fetang 100 tse tswang dinaheng tse batlang ho ba 30, hammoho le UN, OECD le EU, tlaleho ena e ikemetseng e kopanya bopaki ba mahlale ba hajwale ka bokgoni le dikotsi tsa AI e hodimo — e hlokomedisa hore disistimi tse ding hona jwale di ka lemoha ha di ntse di lekolwa mme tsa fetola boitshwaro ba tsona ka moo.",
