  "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” now published in English as the canonical edition; the Chinese original manuscript remains available and both versions cross-link.": "‘AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer’ hona jwale e phatlaladitswe ka Senyesemane e le kgatiso e nepahetseng; mongolo wa mantlha wa Sechaena o dula o fumaneha mme livesene tse pedi di hokahantswe.",
  "“Protocolized Openness” confirmed as an English-language paper (with Chinese parallel passages) — no separate translation planned.": "‘Protocolized Openness’ e netefaditswe e le pampiri ya puo ya Senyesemane (e nang le ditemana tse tsamayang hammoho tsa Sechaena) — ha ho na phetolelo e arohaneng e reriloeng.",
